= 1228: Probabilistic Graphical Models
[https://nr.informatik.uni-freiburg.de/people/joschka-boedecker Prof. Joschka Boedecker] and [https://haozhu10015.github.io Hao Zhu], [https://uni-freiburg.de/ University of Freiburg]

This page was created for posting some useful material for the course /Probabilistic Graphical Models/ developed and taught by Prof. Joschka Boedecker and me starting from 2024.

== Announcements
- Welcome to 1228: Probabilistic Graphical Models, Summer semester 2026.
- This course will be taught by Joschka Boedecker, Shengchao Yan, and Hao Zhu.
- Lectures are Tuesdays 16:15--17:45, Building 101, SR 01-016/18. The first lecture is 21 April.
- Exercise sessions will be announced as the semester progresses.
- This webpage contains basic course information; up to date and detailed information will be posted on ILIAS.

